<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Pencils on RaihnForge</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/tags/pencils/</link><description>Recent content in Pencils on RaihnForge</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Nov 2010 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/tags/pencils/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Daily Sketches–nShadowninja &amp;amp; A Tree</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/study/daily-sketchesnshadowninja-a-tree/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Nov 2010 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/study/daily-sketchesnshadowninja-a-tree/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/2010_nshadowsong.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/2010_nshadowsong.jpg" alt="2010_nshadowsong" title="2010_nshadowsong">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>This sketch was of a aggressive ninja ready for an attack!&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/2010_a_tree.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/2010_a_tree.jpg" alt="2010_a_tree" title="2010_a_tree">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I don’t often draw environment subjects, but since I have begun work on my Indie gaming project I have become much more interested in scenery.  This tree formed from some fun curves that I sketched on a paper while doodling one day.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>SC Concept Sketching</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/study/concept-sketching/</link><pubDate>Tue, 14 Sep 2010 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/study/concept-sketching/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/SC-Concept-Sketching_205C/Mass-Thors.png">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/wordpress/raihn/images/SC-Concept-Sketching_205C/Mass-Thors_thumb.png" alt="Mass Thors" title="Mass Thors">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I have been working on some sketches over the last week.  They are inspired by watching some Starcraft 2 games on GOMtv.  The concepts are for possible T-Shirt ideas, or otherwise just fun imagery related to the game play and culture.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/wp-imports/art/rofl_stomp.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/wp-imports/art/rofl_stomp_thumb.jpg" alt="rofl_stomp" title="rofl_stomp">&lt;/a>       &lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/wp-imports/art/firebear_cute.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/wp-imports/art/firebear_cute_thumb.jpg" alt="firebear_cute" title="firebear_cute">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/wp-imports/art/firebear_study.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/wp-imports/art/firebear_study_thumb.jpg" alt="firebear_study" title="firebear_study">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I Korea the Marauder has a funny translation that means close to Fire bear, as I understand it.  Very fun imagining the FIre bears!&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Revenge of Lil' Red Riding Hood</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/illustration/revenge-of-lil-red-riding-hood/</link><pubDate>Sat, 01 Sep 2007 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/illustration/revenge-of-lil-red-riding-hood/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/2007_revenge-of-red-riding-hood.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/2007_revenge-of-red-riding-hood.jpg" alt="2007_revenge of red riding hood" title="2007_revenge of red riding hood">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I drew as a fun riff off of the old fable of little red riding hood.  She is all grown up now, and seeking revenge for her grandmother by slaying all the were wolfs in the land.  I hope to color this sketch at some point.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>